document_data.name: Emilo Haversack
document_data.mainbody:
'''Emilo Haversack''' was a [[kender]] from the world of [[Krynn]].

{{quote|''He's a short person with clever hands and a quick wit who's been thrust under mysterious circumstances into my [[priest]]'s life. I can't help but wonder what will come of it."''|[[Finder Wyvernspur]]}}
document_data.Physical description: He had pointed ears and his hair was drawn up into a topknot. His brown hair was streaked with gray.
